The man looks up from his newspaper when he 
notices you staring. "Have you read this?" he 
exclaims, shaking the latest edition of "The Last 
Word" in your face. "It says here the wizard's 
corruption has spread as far as Oston to the 
south, and New Console is completely 
unrecoverable! These are dangerous times," he 
mutters, shaking his head and turning back to his 
reading.
